974
01:19:10,206 --> 01:19:11,738
Lewat sini. Bangun!

975
01:19:32,795 --> 01:19:34,661
Masuklah, cepat!

976
01:19:34,663 --> 01:19:35,762
Terima kasih, Mademoiselle!

977
01:19:46,175 --> 01:19:49,943
Aku khawatir konsernya selesai
lebih lama dari perkiraan.

978
01:19:49,945 --> 01:19:51,945
Selamat malam.
Tuhan memberkati.

979
01:20:03,592 --> 01:20:05,826
Benjamin dan Leah?/
Di loteng jerami.

980
01:20:05,828 --> 01:20:06,960
Lalu sisanya?

981
01:20:07,963 --> 01:20:09,029
Bersembunyi..

982
01:20:09,031 --> 01:20:10,564
