Diam, Jo.
Dia butuh tidur.

984
01:20:27,016 --> 01:20:29,082
Kau akan di Spanyol
esok hari.

985
01:20:32,288 --> 01:20:33,554
Tidak.

986
01:20:35,991 --> 01:20:38,959
Aku akan bawa anak-anak
ke perbatasan, lalu kembali.

987
01:20:43,299 --> 01:20:44,631
Dia semakin dekat.

988
01:20:45,334 --> 01:20:46,633
Bisa kurasakan.

989
