1051
01:28:51,820 --> 01:28:53,153
Apa semua mengikutiku?

1052
01:28:54,657 --> 01:28:56,323
Jo?

1053
01:28:56,325 --> 01:28:59,326
Sepertinya katu tidak bersama kami
sepanjang pagi ini.

1054
01:28:59,328 --> 01:29:02,663
Sementara aku menghargai
kau bukan ahli matematika alami, aku..

1055
01:29:02,665 --> 01:29:04,798
Jo!

1056
01:29:04,800 --> 01:29:06,266
Jo! Jo!/
Ada apa, Hubert?

1057
01:29:06,268 --> 01:29:09,736
Jo!

1058
01:29:12,408 --> 01:29:14,074
Kalian semua,
diam di tempat.

1059
01:29:33,929 --> 01:29:37,264
Apa kau Yahudi?/
Benar.

1060
01:29:37,266 --> 01:29:39,466
Kau akan diantar ke stasiun
oleh Kopral Hoffman.

1061
01:29:41,203 --> 01:29:42,302
Ambilkan mereka kuda.

1062
01:29:43,906 --> 01:29:45,038
Kau seorang Kopral?

1063
01:29:47,409 --> 01:29:49,376
Demi tuhan,
kau mau mereka berjalan?

1064
01:29:49,378 --> 01:29:50,477
Mereka bisa pakai kudaku.

1065
01:29:51,413 --> 01:29:53,113
Maukah kau ambilkan dia?

1066
01:29:53,115 --> 01:29:54,414
Sekarang, Jo Lalande.

1067
01:30:57,346 --> 01:30:58,945
Lalu?

1068
01:30:58,947 --> 01:31:00,213
Itu bukan urusanku.

1069
